Review: Laughed so hard I cried. Pure gold.

An absolute triumph. Every bit as phenomenal as the first film. Possibly better. A beautiful continuation of the legend of the Black Panther filled to the brim with stunning performances. And at its heart a loving tribute to Chadwick Boseman’s legacy. The Black Panther lives! Wakanda Forever!
Like a moth to the flame, consumed by the fire.
Jackie Chan and Michelle Yeoh deliver in this mind blowing action packed adventure filled with amazing practical stunts.
A fantastic popcorn buddy action comedy, without the copaganda. And a top tier kung fu flick. Exceptional martial arts fight choreography. An absolute delight! Highly recommend the director’s cut!
